{"name": "vf3py", "metadata": {"name": "vf3py", "version": "0.0.7", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Interfacing Python and NetworkX with VF3 \u2013 the fastest algorithm for graph/subgraph isomorphism calculation", "upload_time": 1733999160}, "documentation": ["# VF3Py\n\nInterfacing Python and NetworkX with VF3 \u2013 the fastest algorithm for graph/subgraph isomorphism calculation.\n\n## Setup\n\nMake sure that your OS is either Linux or Windows. For Linux, you need to have Python >= 3.7. For Windows, you need to have Python >= 3.8.\n\nVF3Py can be installed using this command:\n\n```\npip install vf3py\n```\nTest your installation:\n\n```\n$ python\n>>> import vf3py.test\n>>> vf3py.test.run_tests()\n(...lots of output...)\nOK\n>>> \n```\n\n## Documentation\n\n[![pipeline status](https://gitlab.com/knvvv/vf3py/badges/master/pipeline.svg)](https://gitlab.com/knvvv/vf3py/-/commits/master)\n\nAvailable [here](https://knvvv.gitlab.io/vf3py)\n\n\n## Other projects that use VF3Py\n\nFor now, all projects are mine:\n\n* [algebra_repr](https://gitlab.com/knvvv/algebra_repr) (TODO: come up with a better name) -- uses SageMath to construct finite algebraic structures (groups, rings, fields), then represents them as graphs. Graph isomorphism allows to check if any two algebraic structures are isomorphic or not.\n\n* [PyXYZ](https://gitlab.com/knvvv/pyxyz) -- A Python Library for Molecular Geometry Manipulation. TODO: Use VF3Py to generate automorphisms groups for molecular graphs.\n\n\n## Links\n\n[Gitlab home page](https://gitlab.com/knvvv/vf3py)\n\n[VF3Py PyPi page](https://pypi.org/project/vf3py)\n\n[Original VF3 implementation](https://github.com/MiviaLab/vf3lib)\n\n\n## References\n\n1. Challenging the time complexity of exact subgraph isomorphism for huge and dense graphs with VF3 - Carletti V., Foggia P., Saggese A., Vento M. - IEEE transactions on pattern analysis and machine intelligence - 2018\n2. Introducing VF3: A new algorithm for subgraph isomorphism - Carletti V., Foggia P., Saggese A., Vento M. - International Workshop on Graph-Based Representations in Pattern Recognition - 2017\n3. Comparing performance of graph matching algorithms on huge graphs - Carletti V., Foggia P., Saggese A., Vento M. - Pattern Recognition Letters - 2018\n4. A Parallel Algorithm for Subgraph Isomorphism - V. Carletti, P. Foggia, P. Ritrovato, M. Vento, V. Vigilante - International Workshop on Graph-Based Representations in Pattern Recognition - 2019\n"], "modules": [{"name": "vf3py.test.edge_test", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "vf3py.test.edge_test.same_edge", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "n1_attrib", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "n2_attrib", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.edge_test.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "verbose", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "vf3py.test.edge_test.VERBOSE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.mono", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "vf3py.test.mono.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Hardcoded sanity check test case."]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "vf3py.test.run_tests", "xref": {"fqname": "vf3py.test.test_driver.run_tests", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "vf3py.test.test_driver", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "vf3py.test.test_driver.run_tests", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.basic_graphs", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "vf3py.test.basic_graphs.networkx_isomorphisms", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "G", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.basic_graphs.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "verbose", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "vf3py.test.basic_graphs.TEST_GRAPHS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.basic_graphs.CRASH_GRAPHS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.basic_graphs.VERBOSE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.mol_isoms", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "vf3py.test.mol_isoms.sdf_to_graph", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "sdf_fname", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "nx.Graph", "xref": {"fqname": "networkx.Graph", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.mol_isoms.same_element", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "n1_attrib", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "n2_attrib", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vf3py.test.mol_isoms.get_hcarbon_subgraph", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "graph", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "nx.Graph", "xref": {"fqname": "networkx.Graph", "project": null}, "params": null}, "docum